EXAMPLE OF PERFECT OUTPUT:
[MARKER :: Professional Experience]
[:B:]Senior DevOps Engineer[:/B:][:BR:]
[:B:]Cloud Solutions Inc. | Dallas, TX[:/B:][:TAB:][:B:]2019 - Present[:/B:][:BR:]
[:L1:] Spearheaded migration of 200+ legacy apps to Kubernetes, reducing costs by 30%.
[:L1:] Implemented CI/CD pipelines using GitHub Actions and Terraform.

[MARKER :: Education]
[:B:]University of Texas[:/B:] [:PIPE:] Bachelor of Science in Computer Science [:PIPE:] 2018
[/MARKER]

GOAL: Professional, structured, high-fidelity resume with zero data residue.
